		rts
		
;---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
;	CompareAndCache
;		Once we've sucessfully tokenized one of the separators we use this routine to compare
;		the new token against the stuff already in the cache
;		if the new token is not there it is cached
;
;		REGISTERS
;			INPUT
;				a2		-	Ptr to cache	
